Global Electrosurgical Smoke Evacuation Systems Market Insights
Electrosurgical Smoke Evacuation Systems Market size was valued at USD 0.35 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.60 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Electrosurgical Smoke Evacuation Systems Market Overview
The global electrosurgical smoke evacuation systems market was valued at USD 226.5 million in 2024 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 7.6% from 2025 to 2032. This growth is primarily driven by the increasing adoption of minimally invasive surgeries and growing concerns regarding the health risks associated with electrosurgical smoke. Hospitals, ambulatory surgical centers, and outpatient clinics are the primary end-users of these systems, while North America holds a dominant market share. The demand for electrosurgical smoke evacuation systems is further fueled by advancements in technology, the rising prevalence of chronic diseases, and increasing healthcare expenditures globally.

